<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Van Mite La</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thimin lei a tuom laiin,
 Van vakin piellei a salh;
 Van zaila hawih a hung gii,
 'Cham leng hen&quot; ti'n la a sau.

[V2]
 &quot;Chungnung penah Pathien chu,
 Lopi takin um henla
 Lei chunga mite lakah,
 'Cham leng hen' tin la a sau.

[V3]
 2. Silhpuon vam lopi silh in
 Bethlehem daikieng achun;
 Hukdampa ding hung pieng chu,
 Chawihatna la thak a sau'

[V4]
 3. Van mite a chieh taua,
 Thangvan sang a kaih nungun;
 Belampute thawmhau in.
 Bethlehem dai a ngak ui.

[V5]
 4. Keihaw le aw van mite.
 Belampute mahbang khan;
 &quot;Leiah chamna leng hen&quot; tin,
 La ei sak pih lo ding maw?</lyrics>
<author>Doh Is C Upa Rokhum</author>
<hymn_number>21</hymn_number>
</song>